From Gerald Olchowy Subject Re RUMOUR Keenan signs with Rangers In article Gary L Dare writes Interestingly Keenan's co coach or is it his Number One on Team Canada at the World Championships is Roger But ultimately their hockey philosophies are like night and Keenan believes in pressuring the opposition and taking the initiative within the limits of his system Roger has a reactive hockey is why Messier will be able to and has played for Keenan but thought Roger's way was a sure It'd be interesting if the Rangers call in the balance of Neilsen's contract to be Keenan's assistant Roger did do a very good job with the mediocre players just as he handled the Cinderella Canucks of years ago but his mistake was playing the Rangers like those Canucks last May Roger is a great assistant considering what must be bad blood between Nielson and Messier it would be a mistake to bring him back even in that Gerald